for 1 lbs beef cubes

combine in food processor
 - 1 chopped onion
 - 30 g peanut butter
 - 1 tbsp tomato paste
 - 1 tbsp olive oil
 - 2 tsp ground allspice
 - 1/2 tsp salt
 - 1/2 tsp black pepper
 - 1/4 tsp crushed pepper
 - 1/4 tsp ginger

 serve with
  - flat bread
  - tomatoes
  - raw onions

